products.title: Meadow Dove Grey 89mm Vertical Blind
products.metadescription: Meadow dove grey 89mm vertical blind in grey. Made to measure from 18.18 with free uk mainland delivery. This 89mm vertical blind includes 5-year guarantee and child safety features.
products.productdescription:
Add a chic touch of decoration to your windows and complement a modern scheme with this print of flora in cool grey and white tones. The meadow dove vertical blind will bring both comfort and classic style to your space thanks to the graceful motif displayed on pollergen treated fabric.
 
 Product id: db-vtb1427 fabric colour: dove grey material: 100% polyester headrail: white slimline headrail supported by white steel brackets - top or face fixable   slat width: 89mm control type: smooth chain operation with cord tilt or wand tilt and pull energy saving rating: er2 - medium energy saving value - effective thermal retention light filtering: yes
